## 🏗️ Architecture Overview

### Project Structure
```
lib/
├── main.dart                      # Entry point
├── models/
│   ├── ble_device_model.dart     # Device data model
│   └── vital_data_model.dart     # Health vitals model
├── providers/
│   ├── ble_provider.dart         # BLE state management
│   └── theme_provider.dart       # Theme management
├── screens/
│   ├── scan_screen.dart          # Device scanning UI
│   ├── device_detail_screen.dart # Device details & live data
│   └── vitals_dashboard_screen.dart # Charts & analytics
├── widgets/
│   ├── device_tile.dart          # Reusable device list item
│   ├── connection_status.dart    # Connection indicator
│   ├── characteristic_tile.dart  # Characteristic display
│   └── vital_chart.dart          # Real-time chart widget
└── utils/
    ├── ble_utils.dart            # BLE helper functions
    ├── permission_handler.dart   # Permission management
    └── constants.dart            # App constants
```

### Architecture Pattern: **MVVM + Provider**

```
┌─────────────┐
│    View     │ (UI Screens)
│  (Screens)  │
└──────┬──────┘
       │
       ▼
┌─────────────┐
│  ViewModel  │ (Providers)
│ (Providers) │
└──────┬──────┘
       │
       ▼
┌─────────────┐
│    Model    │ (Data Models)
│   (Models)  │
└──────┬──────┘
       │
       ▼
┌─────────────┐
│   Service   │ (flutter_reactive_ble)
│    (BLE)    │
└─────────────┘
```

### Key Components

#### 1. **BLE Provider** (`ble_provider.dart`)
Manages all BLE operations:
- Device scanning
- Connection management
- Service/characteristic discovery
- Data subscription
- Auto-reconnect logic

#### 2. **Theme Provider** (`theme_provider.dart`)
Handles app theming:
- Light/Dark mode switching
- Persistent theme storage

#### 3. **Models**
- `BleDeviceModel`: Encapsulates device information
- `VitalDataModel`: Structures health vital readings

